Because there was an active answering machine at the Pane office/residence, all calls remaining on the line until the answering machine picked up are recorded as completed calls. Pursuant to an order from the court, the Yoknapatawpha County Sheriff's Department obtained the telephone records for Peter Pane's residence telephone number for the period between February 1, 2000 through July 17, 2000.
